      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILLOW'S GIRL (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (23.06) at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. PAW OPPA (7) stalked the lead from a middle box and kept coming to win (22.22) at Ballarat in Grade 5 over 390m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. One of main contenders. COLLECTIVE KAOS (6) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (22.76) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. MORAINE ARNIE (3) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to bounce back.",
